BasicScriptingLanguage Editor was created by Mike Santiago in C# and the .NET Framework. The editor uses the following libraries to make the magic happen
-FastColoredTextBox (https://github.com/PavelTorgashov/FastColoredTextBox) -IniFile (http://www.codeproject.com/Articles/21896/INI-Reader-Writer-Class-for-C-VB-NET-and-VBScript) -BasicScriptingLanguage (https://github.com/Luigifan/BasicScriptingLanguage)
